<section id="custom">
<title>Custom Shortcuts</title>

<p>To create your own keyboard shortcut:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Select <gui>Custom shortcuts</gui> on the left side of the window.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click <key>+</key> on the right.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Provide a <gui>Name</gui> for the shortcut, and a <gui>Command</gui> to
      be run, then click <gui>Apply</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click <gui>Disabled</gui> on the far right.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Hold down the desired key combination.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

</section>

